Title: Warabigami: Ten no Komoriuta
Description: ['Music video for the song ', Warabigami: Ten no Komoriuta, " by Junko Yamamoto that was featured on NHK's Minna no Uta program. The song is a cover of Okinawan singer Misako Koja's ", Warabigami, '. The video features illustrations by Okinawan artist Nakachi Nobuhide.']
